modules.description: This module draws 2D triangular meshes and visualizes level curves or regions based on scalar values defined on the mesh. It operates on mesh data structures along with associated scalar fields, supporting operations like mesh rendering, point and triangle indexing, Voronoi diagram overlay, and level set visualization. Concrete use cases include scientific visualization of finite element solutions, terrain elevation maps, and 2D function contouring using customizable colors and display dimensions.
